JUNCTION_POINTS: Points where flowlines converge or diverge.
GEOM_DGOS: Discrete Geographic Objects - The valley bottom split into a sampling frame of polygons where the IGO points are at the center of each polygon.
GEOM_IGOS: Integrated Geographic Objects - Points placed at a specified distance interval along the valley centerline. This distance is a function of the average valley width for a given stream.
DGO_BEAVER: Beaver/BRAT related metrics calculated for DGOs.
DGO_IMPACTS: Metrics related to anthropological impacts for DGOs.
DGO_VEG: Vegetation metrics for DGOs calculated from LANDFIRE.
IGO_BEAVER: Beaver/BRAT related metrics calculated for IGOs.
IGO_IMPACTS: Metrics related to anthropological impacts for IGOs.
IGO_VEG: Vegetation metrics for IGOs calculated from LANDFIRE
DGO_METRICS: Combination of all of the different thematic metrics attributed to the DGOs.
IGO_METRICS: Combination of all of the different thematic metrics attributed to the IGOs.
